VIRGIL BROWN v. STATE OF FLORIDA 21 So. (2nd) 715

January Term, 1945

April 13, 1945 Division A Jones & Latham, for appellant. J. Tom Watson, Attorney General, and Sumter Leitner, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The record and the briefs in this cause have been examined and we find no reversible error.

Affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
